<%- include ("../partials/header.ejs") %>
<body>
  <header>
      <%- include ("../partials/ennavbar.ejs") %>
  </header>
  
  <section class="banner">
    <ol class="breadcrumb">
      <li class="breadcrumb-item">
        <a href="/en" class="text-decoration-none">Home</a>
      </li>
      <li class="breadcrumb-item active">About us</li>
    </ol>
    <div class="container">
      <img class="img_bg" src="/uploads/logopag.png" alt="Responsive image" width="100%">
    </div>
  </section>

  <section>
    <div class="container column">
      <h2 class="align-self-center">Penumbra Games</h2>
        <p  align="justify">Penumbra Games is a Brazilian indie game development studio created in September 2019 along with the idea of ​​Vernesis, this being our first of many games.</p>
        <p  align="justify">Our team is made up of talented game lovers who are driven by an intense passion for digital entertainment. We seek to bring a combination of innovative and exciting mechanics to the 2D world, where we will create games that everyone can be proud to play.</p>
        <p align="justify">We believe that the gaming universe is much more than digital entertainment. For us, this universe is not only capable of bringing fun, but it is also where you can make friends, create unique moments and even learn important things to use on a daily basis.</p>
      </div>
  </section>

  <section class="team">
    <div class="container column mb-4">
      <div class="column">
        <h2 class="align-self-center">Our team</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="flexWrap">
        <div class="card">
          <div class="card_title">
            <img class="card-img-top rounded" src="/uploads/kaio.jpg" alt="">
            <h4 class="card-title">Kaio Borges</h4>
          </div>
          <div class="card_body">
            <h6 class="card-subtitle mb-2 text-muted" align="center">Programmer and Game Design</h6>
            <p class="card-text text-justify">Kaio Borges is responsible for all lines of code in the projects. Since he was young, he always had a lot of contact with games and technology, resulting in entering a graduation in the area and studying a lot about game development. He is currently an Information Systems student at the State University of Bahia and with Rafael Araújo, brought together the team called Penumbra Games.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
  
        <div class="card">
          <div class="card_title">
            <img class="card-img-top rounded" src="/uploads/logopenumbra.png" alt="">
            <h4 class="card-title">Rafael Araújo</h4>
          </div>
          <div class="card_body">
            <h6 class="card-subtitle mb-2 text-muted" align="center">Artist & Animation</h6>
              <p class="card-text text-justify">Rafael Araújo is responsible for all the visual part of the projects, with the help of other artists to create the necessary visual identities. A born game lover who has wanted to launch his projects for others to play for a long time, he has already risked on platforms like Byond, creating a Naruto Fan Game. He is currently an Information Systems student and in his spare time, when he is not working, he creates Vernesis creations.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
  
        <div class="card">
          <div class="card_title">
            <img class="card-img-top rounded" src="/uploads/logopenumbra.png" alt="">
            <h4 class="card-title">Ygor Ferrari</h4>
          </div>
          <div class="card_body">
            <h6 class="card-subtitle mb-2 text-muted" align="center">Head Administrator & Composer</h6>
              <p class="card-text text-justify">Ygor Ferrari is responsible for the critical sense of the team's creation and also for the original soundtracks of the projects. Some time ago he ventured into the world of music, learning some instruments such as: Guitar and Piano. Currently, he, in his spare time, creates the wonderful compositions that players will hear in each challenge across different worlds.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
  
        <div class="card">
          <div class="card_title">
            <img class="card-img-top rounded" src="/uploads/guilherme.jpg" alt="">
            <h4 class="card-title">Guilherme Lopes</h4>
          </div>
          <div class="card_body">
            <h6 class="card-subtitle mb-2 text-muted" align="center">Artist & Animation</h6>
            <p class="card-text text-justify">Guilherme is a young man who, since he was little, had a lot of contact with the world of the arts, having a great appreciation for this area. Since then he started to use his free time to make drawings and improve his art, first on paper and later with pixel art. In Vernesis, he is responsible for the artistic part, involving the creation of sprites and animations, along with other members of the group. <i class = "fas fa-thumbs-up"> </i></p>
          </div>
        </div>
  
        <div class="card">
          <div class="card_title">
            <img class="card-img-top rounded" src="/uploads/logopenumbra.png" alt="">
            <h4 class="card-title">Matheus Soares</h4>
          </div>
          <div class="card_body">
            <h6 class="card-subtitle mb-2 text-muted" align="center">Head Administrator</h6>
              <p class="card-text text-justify">Matheus Soares is responsible for managing the community inside and outside the game, he is also an active part of creating content. He is a notable and dedicated member who has a great experience in this aspect due to his presence in other games .</p>
          </div>
        </div>
  
        <div class="card">
          <div class="card_title">
            <img class="card-img-top rounded" src="/uploads/logopenumbra.png" alt="">
            <h4 class="card-title">Gabriel Vinícius</h4>
          </div>
          <div class="card_body">
            <h6 class="card-subtitle mb-2 text-muted" align="center">Administrator</h6>
            <p>Gabriel Vinícius is responsible for managing the community in-game and out-of-game, he is also an active part of creating content. In addition to this role, Gabriel is responsible for carrying out some security tests in our company, seeking the greatest comfort and reliability for the players.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  <%- include ("../partials/scripts.ejs")%>
</body>
<%- include ("../partials/footer.ejs") %>